summary: This FBI electronic communication documents the transfer of case files from the Miami office to the Washington Field Office Evidence room on March 4, 2025, for the investigation with case ID 72-MM-113327. It includes an itemized list and FedEx tracking details.

events.title: Transfer of case files to Washington Field Office
events.description: Case files from the investigation were shipped via FedEx from the Miami office to the Washington Field Office Evidence room.

keyFacts: This document is an FBI electronic communication dated March 7, 2025, regarding the transfer of case files.
The files were transferred from Miami to the Washington Field Office Evidence room on March 4, 2025.
The transfer is related to the investigation with case ID 72-MM-113327.
The communication includes an itemized list of contents and FedEx tracking details as enclosures.
